&lt;p&gt;This is a new role in the Quality, Service Improvement &amp; Sustainability team, responsible for the management and provision of high quality information support to a range of service improvement projects across Moorfields Eye Hospital NHS Foundation Trust.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Senior Information Analyst will be responsible for delivering robust analytical support to our projects and Trust wide transformation programmes. Working under direction from the Performance and Information lead, the post holder will deliver analysis on a range of projects, to help identify key benefits, patterns, trends or inconsistencies which could be improved in our services.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Ella Preston Job title Performance and Information Lead - Service Improvement &amp; Sustainability Email address e.preston@nhs.net Telephone number 0207 566 2271&lt;/p&gt;
